"{\"uid\": \"skynews.com.au-lifestyle-new-2-coins-celebrating-australias-olympic-and-paralympic-athletes-released-by-royal-australian-mint-to-mark-paris-2024-news-story-5d49f8b692716375aafa6475b478dd26\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Special $2 coins have been made available to celebrate the Australian athletes competing in the Paris Olympic and Paralympic Games.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 131, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 59, \"end\": 69, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"score\": 0.9778281545106096, \"rank\": 0.020855270872444747, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Australians can now get their hands on new $2 coins which have been released to celebrate the nation's Olympic and Paralympic athletes competing in Paris.\", \"from\": 133, \"to\": 287, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 281, \"end\": 286, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999995909016361, \"rank\": 4.0909860057972934e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Royal Australian Mint have created four coloured uncirculated coins which are individually being made available at participating Woolworths supermarkets.\", \"from\": 289, \"to\": 446, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 293, \"end\": 314, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Royal_Australian_Mint\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Royal Australian Mint\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Royal_Australian_Mint\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Royal_Australian_Mint\"}, {\"begin\": 422, \"end\": 432, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Woolworths_Supermarkets\", \"score\": 0.999890013233137, \"rank\": 0.00010703237280724754, \"text\": \"Woolworths\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Woolworths_Supermarkets\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Woolworths_Supermarkets\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On Wednesday, the first of the coins were issued through the tills.\", \"from\": 448, \"to\": 515, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It is dedicated to the Olympic Team and features the word 'community'.\", \"from\": 516, \"to\": 586, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Another Olympic Team coin featuring 'Allez Aus', the supporter chant for athletes in the Paris games, will be made available on July 31.\", \"from\": 588, \"to\": 724, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 677, \"end\": 682, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999995909016361, \"rank\": 4.0909860057972934e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A third Olympic Team coin with the word 'Olympism' will be issued on August 14, while the Paralympic Team coin will be available on August 28.\", \"from\": 726, \"to\": 868, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"All four coins have an individual design feature, alongside the Olympic-themed wording.\", \"from\": 870, \"to\": 957, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Royal Australian Mint is also offering all Olympic Team coins available for purchase as a three-coin collection set.\", \"from\": 959, \"to\": 1079, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 963, \"end\": 984, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Royal_Australian_Mint\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Royal Australian Mint\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Royal_Australian_Mint\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Royal_Australian_Mint\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Paralympic Team coin can be purchased as a one-coin collection piece.\", \"from\": 1081, \"to\": 1154, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Olympic Games will be held from July 26 to August 11, while the Paralympic Games will take place from August 28 to September 8.\", \"from\": 1156, \"to\": 1287, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Meanwhile, Australia Post confirmed on Wednesday it will release stamps commemorating Australian Olympic gold medal winners.\", \"from\": 1289, \"to\": 1413, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1300, \"end\": 1314, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_Post\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Australia Post\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_Post\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_Post\"}, {\"begin\": 1375, \"end\": 1385, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"score\": 0.9778281545106096, \"rank\": 0.020855270872444747, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Australians can obtain the stamps online within 48 hours of the medal ceremony, and in post office outlets within one week.\", \"from\": 1415, \"to\": 1538, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Recognising athletes on a stamp that is accessible to their families and all Australians is a special tribute,\\\" Australia Post Executive General Manager Retail, Josh Bannister, said.\", \"from\": 1540, \"to\": 1723, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1653, \"end\": 1667, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_Post\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Australia Post\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_Post\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_Post\"}, {\"begin\": 1702, \"end\": 1706, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\", \"score\": 0.9214982402685987, \"rank\": 0.08518606835465974, \"text\": \"Josh\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\"}, {\"begin\": 1707, \"end\": 1716, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roger_Bannister\", \"score\": 0.9999999980832399, \"rank\": 1.6895331459727957e-09, \"text\": \"Bannister\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roger_Bannister\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roger_Bannister\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Whether it be in the pool, track, courtside, on the pitch or in the ring, Aussies can throw their support behind their favourite gold medallists and take home a piece of history with a stamp or coin, sharing the love and excitement for the Paris Olympics.\\\"\", \"from\": 1725, \"to\": 1982, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"To join the conversation, pleaselog in.Do not have an account?Register  Join the conversation, you are commenting asLogout  Our Apps\", \"from\": 1984, \"to\": 2116, \"entities\": []}]}"